quran[21{c,v,t}:
44,19,Allah ke muqablay mein sar kashi nah karo mein tumahray samnay ( apni mamoriyat ki ) Sarih sanad paish karta hon
44,20,aur mein apne rab aur tumahray rab ki panah le chuka hon iss se ke tum mujh par hamla aawar ho
44,21,"agar tum meri baat nahi mantay to mujh par haath daalnay se baz raho """
44,22,aakhir kaar uss ne apne rab ko puraka ke yeh log mujrim hain
44,23,( jawab diya gaya ) acha to raton raat mere bundon ko le kar chal par tum logon ka peecha kya jaye ga
44,24,samandar ko uss ke haal par khula chore day yeh sara lashkar ghark honay wala hai
44,25,""" kitney hi baagh aur chashmay"
44,26,aur khait aur shandaar mehal thay jo woh chore gay
44,27,"kitney hi aish ke sir o samaan, jin mein woh mazay kar rahay thay unn ke peechay dharay reh gay"
44,28,"yeh howa unn ka injaam, aur hum ne dosaron ko inn cheezon ka waris bana diya"
44,29,"phir nah aasman unn par roya nah zameen, aur zara si mohlat bhi un ko nah di gayi"
44,30,iss terhan bani Israel ko hum ne sakht zillat ke azaab
44,31,firaon se nijaat di jo hadd se guzar jaane walon mein fi al waqea barray ounchay darjay ka aadmi tha
44,32,"aur unn ki haalat jantay hue, unn ko duniya ki doosri qomon par tarjeeh di"
44,33,aur unhen aisi nishanain deikhein jin mein Sarih azmaish thi
44,34,yeh log kehte hain
44,35,""" hamari pehli mout ke siwa aur kuch nahi uss ke baad hum dobarah uthaye jaane walay nahi hain"
44,36,"agar tum sachey ho to utha lao hamaray baap dada ko """
44,37,yeh behtar hain ya tba ki qoum aur uss se pehlay ke log? hum ne un ko isi bana par tabah kya ke woh mujrim hogaye thay
44,38,yeh aasman o zameen aur inn ke darmain ki cheeze hum ne kuch khail ke tor par nahi bana di hain
44,39,"inn ko hum ne brhq peda kya hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
